{
  "url": "/cat/lunch-bags-boxes-totes",
  "type": "root",
  "h1": "Custom Lunch Bags, Boxes & Totes for Your Team",
  "metaTitle": "Custom Lunch Bags Boxes Totes | Perfect Imprints",
  "metaDescription": "Branded lunch bags, boxes & totes for corporate events, employee gifts & safety programs. Customize with your logo. Fast turnaround. Shop now.",
  "introHtml": "<p>Marketing directors planning a trade show giveaway, HR directors putting together an employee onboarding kit, and safety managers outfitting a crew with durable coolers all need practical, everyday promotional products. Custom lunch bags, boxes & totes fit the bill. They keep meals fresh, drinks cold, and gear organized — all while displaying your logo prominently.</p><p>This category includes insulated lunch totes, classic metal lunch boxes, budget-friendly bags, and heavy-duty coolers. Products like the <em>Lunch Tote</em> and <em>Ombré Lunch Tote</em> offer a stylish profile, while the <em>Link Lunch Cooler</em> and <em>9-Can Lunch Cooler</em> provide serious insulation for long shifts. For a retro vibe, the <em>Retro Lunch Box</em> and <em>Thin Retro Lunch Box</em> are crowd-pleasers. The <em>6 Pack Cooler Lunch Bag</em> doubles as a beverage carrier for team outings. Every item can be screen-printed or embroidered with your company name, logo, or message.</p><p>Perfect Imprints makes ordering easy for bulk buyers. Choose from dozens of colors and materials, request a quote for your quantity, and receive a digital proof before production. Most orders ship within 10 business days. Whether you need 50 units for a small team or 5,000 for a national campaign, you’ll find the right combination of price and quality here.</p>",
  "faqs": [
    {
      "q": "What is the minimum order quantity for custom lunch bags?",
      "a": "Minimum order quantities vary by product. Most standard lunch totes and coolers start at 50 pieces, while budget-friendly options may require as few as 25. Contact us for a specific quote on your desired quantity."
    },
    {
      "q": "Can I get my logo screen printed or embroidered?",
      "a": "Yes, both screen printing and embroidery are available. Screen printing works best for simple, bold designs on most materials. Embroidery adds a premium look and is ideal for fabric totes and bags. We’ll help you choose the best method for your logo."
    },
    {
      "q": "How long does production and shipping take?",
      "a": "Standard production takes 5-10 business days after proof approval. Shipping time depends on your location and chosen method. Rush orders are often available for an additional fee. We’ll provide a clear timeline with your quote."
    },
    {
      "q": "Can I order a sample before placing a bulk order?",
      "a": "Absolutely. We offer sample requests for most products. You can order a blank sample to evaluate size, material, and quality. If you need a customized sample, we can produce one for a fee that is typically credited back on the bulk order."
    },
    {
      "q": "Are these lunch bags and coolers insulated?",
      "a": "Most items in this category are insulated. The Link Lunch Cooler, 9-Can Lunch Cooler, and 6 Pack Cooler Lunch Bag feature thick foam insulation to keep food and drinks cold for hours. Some totes and boxes have lighter insulation or none — check product details for specifications."
    }
  ],
  "heroAltText": "Custom lunch bags boxes totes: a branded lunch tote and retro lunch box with company logo on display",
